# Interview Questions

## What is an AWS Region?

A geographical location where AWS operates multiple Availability Zones.

---

## What is an Availability Zone?

One or more physically separate data centers within an AWS Region.

---

## Why does AWS have multiple Availability Zones?

To provide High Availability and Fault Tolerance.

---

## What is an Edge Location?

A location that caches and delivers content closer to users.

---

